name: BMO US TIPS Index ETF
longDescription: The ETF has been designed to replicate, to the extent possible, the performance of the Bloomberg US Treasury Inflation-Linked Bond Index (Series-L), net of expenses. The Fund invests in US Treasury Inflation Protected Securities (TIPS) with at least one year remaining to maturity. Securities held in the Index are generally issued or guaranteed by the U.S. Treasury.
